# Social Media Do’s and Don’ts Checklist 

#✅ Do’s
1.Be mindful of your audience before posting
2.Keep your profiles updated and professional
3.Give credit when sharing others’ content
4.Use strong passwords and enable privacy settings
5.Engage positively and support others online
#❌ Don’ts
1.Do not post when you are angry or emotional
2.Avoid clicking on suspicious links or scams
3.Do not ignore privacy settings on your accounts
4.Avoid spamming or overposting content
5.Do not use social media during important tasks or studies
